text: Today I've brought some interesting products with me, this is part 2 of products under Rs 1K
And we order a lot of products and show you only the tried & tested ones. 4 out of these 5 products are the ones you should definitely try
And one of them is the one you shouldn't buy, because when we ordered it we thought it was good
And as we tested it, it was useless.
Our first product is a telescope, this telescope is under Rs 1K, & generally the quality of cheap telescopes is not that great
But this one is different. You get documentation in the box along with this case. You get a total magnification of 60x
And to adjust the focus, you get a focus ring at the top
I can clearly see the subscribe button through this. And if you go for trekking you also have this compass
You also get 2-3 things as accessories, this is the mount
And if you attach your phone to this, you can also click photos through
And the quality is average keeping the price in mind
So if you don't wanna invest much and want a telescope for looking around at normal things this is a great one
Lets move on to the next one, when we bought this around 2 weeks back it costed around Rs 1K,now the price
Has slightly gone up as it keeps fluctuating
These are great if you're a superhero fan, the sound quality is not what i expected it to be
If you're a Marvel fan, you'll love these. The sound quality is not that great.
It also comes with a 3.5mm cable
Our next product is a laptop stand, these days a lot of people work from home and this is why we included
This portable laptop stand, the laptop keyboard is flat
There are 6 inclinations, & you can adjust them according to your comfort
And this is rubbrised so it wont move or slip down
Now this is a comfortable position. And the quality is good as well
And it costs around Rs 1K, and you can carry this around in your bag as well
The links of the given products are in the description
Our next product is very useful for many
This is not only a power strip but also a USB hub so you can charge multiple products as well
We ordered multiple power strips, but this company Live Tech is a good company
It is compact and the wire quality is too good.
There are 3 ports, so European or Indian plugs you can plug in both of them. And there are 6 USB ports
Also they give 3 cables along with it.
You shouldnt buy our next product, the metaverse is trending right now so i thought I’d order a VR box
But this product is useless cause the quality is not at all good. We tried a lot but we couldnt align the lenses inside this
Seems like they’ve made this in a poor factory
But the rest of the 4 products are good, links are in the description
